<lb n="0185a08"/><head type="no">No. 1077 [Nos. 1075, 1076]</head><div1 type="jing">
<lb n="0185a09"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead><note n="0185004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">【原】麗本，【甲】享和二年刊長谷寺藏本</note>佛說七俱胝佛母心大准提陀羅
<lb n="0185a10"/>尼經</jhead></juan>
<lb n="0185a11"/>
<lb n="0185a12"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0185005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">大唐天竺三藏＝大周沙門【宋】，唐武周沙門【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">大唐天竺三藏＝大周沙門【宋】，＝唐武周沙門【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185005"><lem>大唐天竺三藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">大周沙門</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">唐武周沙門</rdg></app>地婆訶羅譯</byline>
<lb n="0185a13"/><p>爾時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。是時世尊
<lb n="0185a14"/>思惟觀察。<note n="0185006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">愍＋（念）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185006"><lem>愍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">愍念</rdg></app>未來諸眾生故。說是七俱胝佛
<lb n="0185a15"/>母心准提陀羅尼法。即說&CB00057;曰。</p>
<lb n="0185a16"/><p type="dharani">南<note n="0185007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">謨＝無【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185007"><lem>謨</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">無</rdg></app><note n="0185008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">颯＋（蘇臘反）細註【宋】</note><app n="0185008"><lem>颯</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">颯<note place="inline">蘇臘反</note></rdg></app><note n="0185009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">哆＋（都那反）細註【宋】</note><app n="0185009"><lem>哆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">哆<note place="inline">都那反</note></rdg></app>南<note place="inline"><note n="0185010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（奴誓反）＋一【宋】</note><app n="0185010"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">奴誓反一</rdg></app></note>三藐三<note n="0185011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">勃＋（蒲沒反）【宋】</note><app n="0185011"><lem>勃</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">勃蒲沒反</rdg></app>陀俱胝南<note place="inline"><note n="0185012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝同上二句【宋】</note><app n="0185012"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">同上二句</rdg></app></note>
<lb n="0185a17"/><note n="0185013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">怛＋（都捺反）【宋】</note><app n="0185013"><lem>怛</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">怛都捺反</rdg></app><note n="0185014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">姪＋（徒列反）【宋】</note><app n="0185014"><lem>姪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">姪徒列反</rdg></app>他<note place="inline"><note n="0185015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（長引）＋三【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185015"><lem>三</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">長引三</rdg></app></note>唵折戾<note place="inline"><note n="0185016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（之熱反）＋四【宋】</note><app n="0185016"><lem>四</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">之熱反四</rdg></app></note>主戾<note place="inline"><note n="0185017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">五＝同上五句【宋】</note><app n="0185017"><lem>五</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">同上五句</rdg></app></note>准<note n="0185018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">締＝提【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185018"><lem>締</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">提</rdg></app><note place="inline"><note n="0185019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">六＋（句）【宋】</note><app n="0185019"><lem>六</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">六句</rdg></app></note><note n="0185020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">娑＝莎【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185020"><lem>娑</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">莎</rdg></app>
<lb n="0185a18"/>婆訶<note place="inline"><note n="0185021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七＋（句）【宋】</note><app n="0185021"><lem>七</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">七句</rdg></app></note></p>
<lb n="0185a19"/><p>若有比丘比丘尼優婆塞優婆夷。受持讀誦
<lb n="0185a20"/>此陀羅尼滿八十萬遍無量劫來所造五無間
<lb n="0185a21"/>等。一切諸罪<note n="0185022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔皆〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185022"><lem>皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>悉<note n="0185023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔消〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185023"><lem>消</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0185024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滅＋（無餘）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185024"><lem>滅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">滅無餘</rdg></app>。所在生處皆得
<lb n="0185a22"/>值遇諸佛菩薩。所有資<note n="0185025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＋（隨具）【甲】</note><app n="0185025"><lem>具</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">具隨具</rdg></app>隨意充足。生生
<lb n="0185a23"/>常得出家。具持菩薩律儀淨戒。&M010527;生人天
<lb n="0185a24"/>不墮惡趣。常為諸天之所守護。若有在家善
<lb n="0185a25"/>男女等誦持之者。其家無有災橫病苦之所
<lb n="0185a26"/>惱害。諸有所作無不諧偶。所<note n="0185026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">說＝出【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185026"><lem>說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">出</rdg></app>言<note n="0185027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">語＝教【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0185027"><lem>語</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【甲】" resp="Taisho">教</rdg></app>人皆
<lb n="0185a27"/>信受。若有誦此陀羅尼&CB00057;滿十萬遍。夢中
<lb n="0185a28"/>得見諸佛菩薩聲聞緣覺。自見口中<note n="0185028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">吐＝咄【甲】＊</note><app n="0185028"><lem>吐</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">咄</rdg></app>出黑
<lb n="0185a29"/><note n="0185029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">物＝飯【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185029"><lem>物</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">飯</rdg></app>。若有重罪誦滿二十萬遍。夢中亦見諸
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1077.0185b" n="0185b"/>
<lb n="0185b01"/>佛菩薩。亦<note n="0185030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185030"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>自<note n="0185031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＋（口中）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185031"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">見口中</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0185028"><lem>吐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">咄</rdg></app>出黑<app type="＊" source="0185029"><lem>物</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">飯</rdg></app>。若有五逆
<lb n="0185b02"/><note n="0185032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">罪＋（者）【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0185032"><lem>罪</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【甲】" resp="Taisho">罪者</rdg></app>。不得如是善夢<note n="0185033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之者宜＝現時【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185033"><lem>之者。宜</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">現時</rdg></app>應更誦滿七十
<lb n="0185b03"/>萬遍。是時還得如前之相。乃至夢見<app type="＊" source="0185028"><lem>吐</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【甲】">咄</rdg></app>出
<lb n="0185b04"/>白色<note n="0185034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如酪飯等＝粳米酪飯【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185034"><lem>如酪飯等</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">粳米酪飯</rdg></app>。當知此人即是罪滅。清淨
<lb n="0185b05"/>之相。</p>
<lb n="0185b06"/><p>復次我今說<note n="0185035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">此＝之【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185035"><lem>此</lem><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>大陀羅尼所作之事。若於佛
<lb n="0185b07"/>像前。或於塔前若清淨處。以瞿摩<note n="0185036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">夷＋（唐云牛糞）【宋】，（此云牛糞）【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185036"><lem>夷</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">夷唐云牛糞</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">夷此云牛糞</rdg></app>塗地。
<lb n="0185b08"/>而作方壇隨其大小。復以花香幡蓋<note n="0185037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">飲＝飯【甲】</note><app n="0185037"><lem>飲</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">飯</rdg></app>食
<lb n="0185b09"/><note n="0185038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">燈燭＝燈明燭火【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185038"><lem>燈燭</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">燈明燭火</rdg></app>。隨力所辦而供養之。復&CB00057;香水散於四
<lb n="0185b10"/><note n="0185039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">方＋（及以）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185039"><lem>方</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">方及以</rdg></app>上下以為結<note n="0185040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">界＋（既結界已）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185040"><lem>界</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">界既結界已</rdg></app>。於壇四角及壇中央。皆
<lb n="0185b11"/>各置一香水之瓶。持&CB00057;之者於其壇中。面向
<lb n="0185b12"/>東方<note n="0185041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">胡＝&CB00566;【甲】</note><app n="0185041"><lem>胡</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00566;</rdg></app>跪。誦&CB00057;一千<note n="0185042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">八＋（十）【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185042"><lem>八</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">八十</rdg></app>遍。其香水瓶即便
<lb n="0185b13"/>自<note n="0185043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">轉＝輪【甲】</note><app n="0185043"><lem>轉</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">輪</rdg></app>。叉手捧雜花。&CB00057;<note n="0185044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一）＋千【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185044"><lem>千</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">一千</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0185042"><lem>八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">八十</rdg></app>遍。散一鏡面。
<lb n="0185b14"/>又於鏡前正<note n="0185045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">觀＋（鏡面）【宋】【元】【甲】</note><app n="0185045"><lem>觀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【甲】" resp="Taisho">觀鏡面</rdg></app>。誦&CB00057;亦<app type="＊" source="0185044"><lem>千</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">一千</rdg></app><app type="＊" source="0185042"><lem>八</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">八十</rdg></app><note n="0185046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">遍＋（又以香油以蘇摩那花香浸著胡麻油中塗手大指誦&CB00057;一百八遍即於童面鏡中指爪甲內皆各）三十八字【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185046"><lem>遍</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">遍又以香油以蘇摩那花香浸著胡麻油中塗手大指誦&CB00057;一百八遍即於童面鏡中指爪甲內皆各</rdg></app>。得見佛
<lb n="0185b15"/>菩薩像。<note n="0185047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">應＝復誦&CB00057;【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185047"><lem>應</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">復誦&CB00057;</rdg></app>&CB00057;花<note n="0185048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（一）＋百【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185048"><lem>百</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">一百</rdg></app>八遍。而散供<note n="0185049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">養＋（佛菩薩像心所有事一一）十字【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185049"><lem>養</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">養佛菩薩像心所有事一一</rdg></app>。<note n="0185050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔隨〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185050"><lem>隨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>請
<lb n="0185b16"/>問<note n="0185051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔法〕－【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0185051"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>無不決了。若有鬼病以<note n="0185052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00057;＋（&CB00057;）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185052"><lem>&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&CB00057;&CB00057;</rdg></app>茅<note n="0185053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">草＝得香茅第一不得直茅亦得（細註）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><note n="0185053" resp="CBETA" type="mod">草＝（得香茅第一不得直茅亦得）細註【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185053"><lem>草</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">得香茅第一不得直茅亦得</note></rdg></app>而拂
<lb n="0185b17"/>病人即得除愈。若有幼小為鬼所著。以五色
<lb n="0185b18"/>縷應令童女<note n="0185054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">搓＝合【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185054"><lem>搓</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">合</rdg></app>以<note n="0185055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">為＝成【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185055"><lem>為</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">成</rdg></app>線。一&CB00057;一結滿二十
<lb n="0185b19"/><note n="0185056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">一＋（結）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185056"><lem>一</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">一結</rdg></app>。用繫其頸。<note n="0185057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＋（白）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185057"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">以白</rdg></app>芥子&CB00057;<note n="0185058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滿＝之【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185058"><lem>滿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">之</rdg></app>七遍。<note n="0185059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（復）＋散【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185059"><lem>散</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">復散</rdg></app>其面
<lb n="0185b20"/>即便除<note n="0185060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差＝瘥【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185060"><lem>差</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">瘥</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0185b21"/><p>復次有法。於病者<note n="0185061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">前＋（以）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185061"><lem>前</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">前以</rdg></app>墨畫其<note n="0185062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">形＝病人形像【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185062"><lem>形</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">病人形像</rdg></app>。&CB00057;楊枝打
<lb n="0185b22"/><note n="0185063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">之＝此畫形【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185063"><lem>之</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">此畫形</rdg></app>。亦<note n="0185064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">便＝得【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185064"><lem>便</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">得</rdg></app>除<app type="＊" source="0185060"><lem>差</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">瘥</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0185b23"/><p>復<note n="0185065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次有＝有一【宋】【明】【甲】＊</note><app n="0185065"><lem>次有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">有一</rdg></app>法。若有病人為鬼所著身在遠處。
<lb n="0185b24"/>應&CB00057;楊枝<note n="0185066" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">具＝足【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185066"><lem>具</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">足</rdg></app>滿七遍。寄<note n="0185067" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">人＝往【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185067"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">往</rdg></app>持打即亦除
<lb n="0185b25"/><note n="0185068" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">差＝愈【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185068"><lem>差</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">愈</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0185b26"/><p>復<app type="＊" source="0185065"><lem>次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。若在路行<note n="0185069" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦＋（念）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185069"><lem>誦</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">誦念</rdg></app>此&CB00057;。無有賊盜惡
<lb n="0185b27"/>獸等<note n="0185070" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">畏＝怖【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185070"><lem>畏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">怖</rdg></app>。</p>
<lb n="0185b28"/><p>復<app type="＊" source="0185065"><lem>次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。常持此&CB00057;。設有諍訟無不獲勝。
<lb n="0185b29"/>若欲往渡江河大海。誦&CB00057;而渡無有水中惡
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1077.0185c" n="0185c"/>
<lb n="0185c01"/>獸等難。</p>
<lb n="0185c02"/><p>復<app type="＊" source="0185065"><lem>次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。若被繫閉枷鎖<note n="0185071" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禁＋（繫）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185071"><lem>禁</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">禁繫</rdg></app>其身。誦此&CB00057;
<lb n="0185c03"/>者即得解脫。</p>
<lb n="0185c04"/><p>復<note n="0185072" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">次有＝有一【宋】【明】，一【甲】</note><note n="0185072" resp="CBETA" type="mod">次有＝有一【宋】【明】，＝一【甲】</note><app n="0185072"><lem>次有</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">有一</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app>法若諸國土水旱不調。疫毒流<note n="0185073" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＋（應行）【甲】</note><app n="0185073"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">行應行</rdg></app>。
<lb n="0185c05"/>應以酥和胡麻粳米。用手三指取其一撮。&CB00057;
<lb n="0185c06"/>之一遍<note n="0185074" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">置＝擲【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185074"><lem>置</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">擲</rdg></app>火中燒。或經七日七夜。六時如是
<lb n="0185c07"/>相續不絕。一切災疫<note n="0185075" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">悉皆＝無不【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185075"><lem>悉皆</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">無不</rdg></app>消<note n="0185076" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">滅＋（復有一法以酥和稻穀&CB00057;一百八遍火中燒之隨心所願無不成諦財寶增盈求心滿足若人欲令他敬念者稱彼前人名字一&CB00057;一稱滿一百八遍即便敬念）六十一字【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0185076"><lem>滅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">滅復有一法以酥和稻穀&CB00057;一百八遍火中燒之隨心所願無不成諦財寶增盈求心滿足若人欲令他敬念者稱彼前人名字一&CB00057;一稱滿一百八遍即便敬念</rdg></app>。</p>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1077.0186a" n="0186a"/>
<lb n="0186a01"/><p>復<app type="＊" source="0185065"><lem>次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。於河渚間砂潬之上。<note n="0186001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以＋（塗形像）【宋】【明】，（塔形形像）【甲】</note><app n="0186001"><lem>以</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">以塗形像</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">以塔形形像</rdg></app>印。印
<lb n="0186a02"/><note n="0186002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">砂＋（坦上）【宋】，（潬上）【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186002"><lem>砂</lem><rdg wit="【宋】" resp="Taisho">砂坦上</rdg><rdg wit="【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">砂潬上</rdg></app>為塔形像。誦&CB00057;一遍印成一塔。<note n="0186003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（如是數）＋滿【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186003"><lem>滿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">如是數滿</rdg></app>六十
<lb n="0186a03"/>萬遍。<note n="0186004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">或＝即得&CB00418;【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186004"><lem>或</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">即得&CB00418;</rdg></app><note n="0186005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＋（聖者）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186005"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">見聖者</rdg></app>觀<note n="0186006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">世音＝自在【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186006"><lem>世音</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">自在</rdg></app>菩<note n="0186007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩＋（之像）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186007"><lem>薩</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">薩之像</rdg></app>。或見多羅菩薩。
<lb n="0186a04"/><note n="0186008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔或見〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186008"><lem>或見</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>金剛<note n="0186009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">主＝手【甲】</note><app n="0186009"><lem>主</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">手</rdg></app>菩薩。<note n="0186010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">隨＋（其）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186010"><lem>隨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">隨其</rdg></app>心<note n="0186011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">所求＝願【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186011"><lem>所求</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">願</rdg></app>皆得滿足。
<lb n="0186a05"/>或見授與<note n="0186012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">仙＋（神妙）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186012"><lem>仙</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">仙神妙</rdg></app>藥。或見<note n="0186013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">與受＝授與【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186013"><lem>與受</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">授與</rdg></app>菩提之記。</p>
<lb n="0186a06"/><p>復<app type="＊" source="0185065"><lem>次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app><note n="0186014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">法＋（作）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186014"><lem>法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">法作</rdg></app>。右遶菩提樹像。誦&CB00057;滿千萬遍。
<lb n="0186a07"/>即見菩薩為其說法。欲隨菩薩即得隨從。</p>
<lb n="0186a08"/><p>復<app type="＊" source="0185065"><lem>次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。若乞食時常持此&CB00057;。不為惡人惡
<lb n="0186a09"/>狗等類之所<note n="0186015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惱＝侵【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186015"><lem>惱</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">侵</rdg></app>害。<note n="0186016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">若於＝復有一法若在【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186016"><lem>若於</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">復有一法若在</rdg></app>塔前或佛像前或
<lb n="0186a10"/>舍利塔前。誦持此&CB00057;三十萬遍。<note n="0186017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔復〕－【甲】</note><app n="0186017"><lem>復</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>於白月
<lb n="0186a11"/>十五日設大供養。一日一夜不食正<note n="0186018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔念〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186018"><lem>念</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>誦&CB00057;。
<lb n="0186a12"/><note n="0186019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乃至〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186019"><lem>乃至</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得見金剛手菩薩。而彼菩薩即將是
<lb n="0186a13"/><note n="0186020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔人〕－【甲】</note><app n="0186020"><lem>人</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>往於自宮。</p>
<lb n="0186a14"/><p>復<app type="＊" source="0185065"><lem>次有</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【明】【甲】">有一</rdg></app>法。若於轉法輪塔前或佛生處塔前。
<lb n="0186a15"/>或<note n="0186021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">從＝於【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186021"><lem>從</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">於</rdg></app>忉利天下寶階塔前或舍利塔前。於如
<lb n="0186a16"/>是等諸塔之前誦&CB00057;右遶。即見阿&CB00425;羅是多
<lb n="0186a17"/>菩薩及訶利底菩薩。隨其所願皆悉滿足。若
<lb n="0186a18"/>須仙藥即便授之。復為說法示菩薩道。若有
<lb n="0186a19"/>誦此陀羅尼者。乃至未坐道場。一切菩薩<note n="0186022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔常〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186022"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>
<lb n="0186a20"/>為<note n="0186023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">善＝其勝【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186023"><lem>善</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">其勝</rdg></app>友。又此准提大陀羅尼大明&CB00057;法。過去
<lb n="0186a21"/>一切諸佛已說。<note n="0186024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未來一切諸佛當說∞現在一切諸佛今說【宋】【明】，〔未來…說〕八字－【甲】</note><note n="0186024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未來一切諸佛當說∞現在一切諸佛今說【宋】【明】，〔未來一切諸佛當說〕八字－【甲】</note><app n="0186024"><lem>未來一切諸佛當說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">現在一切諸佛今說</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。<note n="0186025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">未來一切諸佛當說∞現在一切諸佛今說【宋】【明】，〔未來…說〕八字－【甲】</note><note n="0186025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">未來一切諸佛當說∞現在一切諸佛今說【宋】【明】</note><app n="0186025"><lem>現在
<lb n="0186a22"/>一切諸佛<note n="0186026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">今＝當【甲】</note><app n="0186026"><lem>今</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">當</rdg></app>說</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">未來一切諸佛當說</rdg></app>。我今亦如是說。為利<note n="0186027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔益〕－【宋】【甲】</note><app n="0186027"><lem>益</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>一
<lb n="0186a23"/>切眾生故。<note n="0186028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔令〕－【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186028"><lem>令</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>得無上菩提故。若有薄福眾
<lb n="0186a24"/>生。<note n="0186029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">無＋（有）【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186029"><lem>無</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">無有</rdg></app>少善根者。無有根器之者。無有<note n="0186030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">菩提分法＝菩提分【宋】【明】，善根分【甲】</note><note n="0186030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">菩提分法＝菩提分【宋】【明】，＝善根分【甲】</note><app n="0186030"><lem>菩提
<lb n="0186a25"/>分法</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】" resp="Taisho">菩提分</rdg><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">善根分</rdg></app>者。若得聞此<note n="0186031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（大准提）＋陀【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186031"><lem>陀</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">大准提陀</rdg></app>羅尼法。速疾證得阿耨
<lb n="0186a26"/>多羅三藐三菩提。若有人<note n="0186032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">能常自憶＝憶持誦【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186032"><lem>能常自憶</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">憶持誦</rdg></app>念。<note n="0186033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">誦持此&CB00057;＝常不懈廢此佛母心大准提陀羅尼者【宋】【明】【甲】</note><app n="0186033"><lem>誦
<lb n="0186a27"/>持此&CB00057;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">常不懈廢此佛母心大准提陀羅尼者</rdg></app>。無量善根皆得成就。佛說此大准提
<lb n="0186a28"/>陀羅尼法時。無量眾生遠塵離垢。得大准提
<lb n="0186a29"/>陀羅尼大明&CB00057;功德。得見十方諸佛菩<note n="0186034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">薩諸＝提【甲】</note><app n="0186034"><lem>薩諸</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">提</rdg></app>
<pb ed="T" id="T20.1077.0186b" n="0186b"/>
<lb n="0186b01"/>聖眾<note n="0186035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">等＝向佛【甲】</note><app n="0186035"><lem>等</lem><rdg wit="【甲】" resp="Taisho">向佛</rdg></app>作禮而去。</p>
<lb n="0186b02"/><juan fun="close" n="001"><jhead><note n="0186036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔大明…寺譯〕三十五字－【宋】【明】【甲】，甲本奧書曰享和二壬戌年五月請得智積院之本更校多本施國訓印板行之豐山長谷沙門快道誌，此經在明藏莫字函新刻似無其功矣享和癸亥三月二十八日一校畢慈順</note><app n="0186036" word-count="35"><lem>大明&CB00057;藏六萬偈中出此七俱胝佛母心大
<lb n="0186b03"/>准提陀羅尼經一卷<note place="inline">垂拱二年於西魏國寺譯</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【明】【甲】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app><note n="0186036" place="foot" type="rest">甲本奧書曰享和二壬戌年五月請得智積院之本更校多本施國訓印板行之豐山長谷沙門快道誌，此經在明藏莫字函新刻似無其功矣享和癸亥三月二十八日一校畢慈順</note></jhead></juan></div1>
